Package: tcrgrapher
Title: R package for identifying condition-associated T cell clones
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Ksenia",
           family = "Lupyr",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "kseniia.lupyr@skoltech.ru")
Description: R package for identifying condition associated T cell clones from a 
    single repertoire. Main function finds clones with significantly high number of
    neighbors (convergent clones or clones with one mismacth), taking into account 
    their generation probabilities.
